175
00:13:09,956 --> 00:13:13,839
That's all I ever asked for! Big deal!

176
00:13:14,246 --> 00:13:15,767
Vishal?

177
00:13:21,930 --> 00:13:25,370
Well, I guess everything's sorted out...

178
00:13:26,030 --> 00:13:27,590
Mum?

179
00:13:37,670 --> 00:13:45,050
We thought we'd come here the moment we found out Colonel Sherali's family lives next door!

180
00:13:45,050 --> 00:13:49,466
It is a great honour indeed.

181
00:13:49,466 --> 00:13:50,976
Of course...

182
00:13:50,976 --> 00:13:54,194
To live in the company of heroes...

183
00:13:54,194 --> 00:13:57,182
