258
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:07,411
Never wanted to. You know it.

259
00:19:07,830 --> 00:19:09,324
So...

260
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:14,549
Your grandfather...

261
00:19:14,549 --> 00:19:17,930
