452
00:33:31,070 --> 00:33:33,060
Waaat wus yisser 'ouse number?

453
00:33:33,060 --> 00:33:35,960
I'll 'av ter git 'is diary...

454
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:41,770
'E used ter write everythin' in 'is diary... Oi'm sure 'e'd 'av de address written somewhere...

455
00:33:41,770 --> 00:33:46,500
Me in-laws used ter talk aboyt Amritsar as if they went dare everyday...

456
00:33:46,500 --> 00:33:53,660
Same 'ere... They talked aboyt Jhelum loike they still lived dare...

457
00:33:54,230 --> 00:33:57,678
Yer ever come 'ere?
-No...

458
00:33:57,678 --> 00:34:01,138
'E never 'ad de time... Typical military man things, yer nu...

459
00:34:01,138 --> 00:34:06,300
Mum an' Da alwus wanted ter visit Jhelum...

460
00:34:06,300 --> 00:34:08,730
Any way they cud...
-Ma'am...

461
00:34:08,730 --> 00:34:09,811
We need eggs for the cake...

462
00:34:09,811 --> 00:34:12,101
We need eggs for the cake...
-Naw, Oi doubt anything's gonna change...

463
00:34:12,101 --> 00:34:14,232
Naw, Oi doubt anything's gonna change...
