464
00:34:14,232 --> 00:34:15,690
You're using up all my balance!

465
00:34:15,690 --> 00:34:17,038
You're using up all my balance!
-Shut up!

466
00:34:17,038 --> 00:34:21,490
Oi want ter 'ear everythin' she's got ter say aboyt Jhelum! So jist shut yer bake, gran'?

467
00:34:21,490 --> 00:34:24,967
Aye, waaat were yer sayin'?

468
00:34:28,040 --> 00:34:35,210
Wud yer luk at de kids the-day... She's 'ere sayin' 'tis enoof for nigh!

469
00:34:35,210 --> 00:34:40,368
She wants 'er dag an' bone back! Naw words for 'er, really!

470
00:34:40,620 --> 00:34:47,280
Back in our day, kids wouldn't even dare tink av commandin' their elders loike dat!

471
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:56,750
Yeah, roi... Oi never dared say a ward meself! Naw idea what's de craic wi' kids the-day...

472
00:34:56,750 --> 00:34:59,601
Jhelum awaits yer wi' open arms...

473
00:34:59,601 --> 00:35:02,361
Cum 'ere sometime?
-Aye.

474
00:35:02,361 --> 00:35:04,700
Ah've alwus wanted ter...

475
00:35:04,700 --> 00:35:08,950
Alwus wanted ter see de place Ah've only 'eard av...

